abstract: Roger Federer defeats Milos Raonic in Brisbane International men's final for 1,000th win of his career; other tennis news noted.
lead_paragraph: Federer notched his 1,000th career victory and collected his 83rd title with a seesawing 6-4, 6-7 (2), 6-4 win over Milos Raonic in the Brisbane International final Sunday in Brisbane, Australia.
